description:
Set 1

Picasso Moon, Friend Of The Devil, Me & My Uncle-> Maggie's Farm, Brown Eyed Women, It's All Over Now, Tennessee Jed, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Eyes Of The World-> Estimated Prophet-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Black Peter-> Around & Around, E: The Mighty Quinn

reviews.review_text: More Marcus Buick Masters! The archive is in short supply of the awesome recordings of Marcus Buick, who spent many nights in the front of board doing hand-held recordings to DAT.  In particular, his 2.26.90 is of the finest quality and deserves wider recognition.

Glorious Estimated Glorious Whoa, glory!

A very under-estimated, yet, profitable show!

Ensemble performance of the band in their more recent halcyon period. Vince and Bruce are in-synch with the newly found vigor of Billy, Mickey, Bobby, Philly, Mickey and scuba diving Jerry.
